BundleWorks is a program to tell the computer which redpower wire to activate / deactivate.

For example: you write red then the red wire which connects to the bundled wire which connects to the computer will be on. Write red again and it will turn off.

commands:
colors such as : red,cyan,blue,lightgray,yellow etc.
reset- turn all the wires off
all - turn all the wires on
break - shutdowns the terminal

Important: Bundleworks assumes you have the regular bundled cable, connected to the back of the computer for output. 